{
  "stem": "20978.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was-- it was a nice life, until the Nazis got stronger, and when we come out of shul, we used to got into fights, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used to attack us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would beat you, you know, take sticks or stones, they throw at you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] That was when the Nazis came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the Hungarians, of course, sided with them, you know, the Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That happened before, yes, the fascists, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Less-- as an individual level?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fights, you know, dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you had a payos, they pulled on it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I personally was stuck into a pile of snow head first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a-- I was a fighter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never turned the other cheek, or run away from a good fight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a big boy for my age, and-- and very nervy, and I fought back, and especially if it had to do to protect my sister.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, when she came out of school or she would be attacked, I was right there to protect her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pesach, I remember very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- before Pesach I was bitten by a dog.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- the matzah factory was in a basement of our school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Europe, matzah was a novelty, you know, when Pesach came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we would, kids come out of school, we would go to the basement window and ask, can I have a piece of matzah?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this dog was roaming around, and somehow I kicked it or chased it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the dog chased me, and caught me, and bit me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Pesach was a nice, nice yontif.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father had Seder, sit on a pillow, put on a kettle.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
